# Basics

# Submodules

## `git submodule add {git url} {path}`
+ Adds a submodule from {git url} to {path}

## `git submodule update [--init] [--recursive]`
+ Update submodules
++ --init initializes submodules if necessary
++ --recursive if the submodule has submodules, initialize them as well

## `git deinit {path}`
+ Removes a git submodule from the current working tree, but doesn't clear references

## `git rm {path}`
+ Removes references to a submodule, and removes it from the working tree, but doesn't clear config


